Interface ICorfuSMRProxyInternal<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICorfuSMRProxy<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CorfuCompileProxy
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface ICorfuSMRProxyInternal<T>
extends ICorfuSMRProxy<T>
    An internal interface to the SMR Proxy.

    This interface contains methods which are used only by Corfu's object layer, and shouldn't be exposed to other packages (such as the annotation processor).

    Created by mwei on 11/15/16.
